OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,FThe PSNI will do "everything" in its
OL,7,Fpower to address the "profound
OL,8,Fsocietal issue" of violence against
OL,9,Fwomen and girls, the force's Chief
OL,10,FConstable has said.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, Jon Boutcher said
OL,13,Fofficers in the major investigation
OL,14,Fteam are handling more than three
OL,15,Ftimes the cases recommended, while
OL,16,Fthose dealing with "offender
OL,17,Fmanagement" including restraining
OL,18,Forders are responsible for double the
OL,19,Fcases they would ideally be.
OL,26,@nD@ROUnD@]O]oD@VOUpD@OO]xD@TOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,FThe head of the PSNI was addressing
OL,7,Fthe policing board, in the context
OL,8,Fthat two women have been killed in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland since their last
OL,10,Fpublic meeting in early March.
OL,12,FLast week a man appeared in court
OL,13,Fcharged with the murder of Amy Doherty
OL,14,Fin Londonderry, while another man
OL,15,Fappeared in court charged with the
OL,16,Fmurder of Ellie Flanagan in Fermanagh
OL,17,Flast month.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,FViolence against women and girls has
OL,7,Falso been under renewed focus as a
OL,8,Fresult of the conviction of Stephen
OL,9,FMcCullagh for the murder of his
OL,10,Fpregnant partner Natalie McNally.
OL,12,FMr Boutcher paid tribute to the
OL,13,FMcNally, Doherty, and Flanagan
OL,14,Ffamilies, as well as the family of
OL,15,FChloe Mitchell, a 21-year-old who was
OL,16,Fkilled in Ballymena in 2023.
OL,18,F"Amy's murder brings to 30 the number
OL,19,Fof women who've been murdered by men
OL,20,Fhere in the past five years," he said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,F"For a country the size of Northern
OL,7,FIreland, that is shocking, and I want
OL,8,Fto reiterate the determination of
OL,9,Feveryone in the PSNI to do everything
OL,10,Fin our power to address this profound
OL,11,Fsocietal issue."
OL,13,FHe added: "I have repeatedly, since
OL,14,Farriving here, expressed concerns
OL,15,Fabout our capacity to properly address
OL,16,Fviolence against women and girls.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@PO]uD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,F"I have also expressed concerns as
OL,7,Fregards to our approach and internal
OL,8,Fmechanisms for dealing with both
OL,9,Fviolence against women and girls and
OL,10,Fmisogyny.
OL,12,F"When arriving I was disturbed by the
OL,13,Fnumbers of domestic homicides in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland and when reaching
OL,15,Finto the behaviour of society in
OL,16,Fgeneral towards women and girls and
OL,17,Finto a small number of cases of
OL,18,Finappropriate behaviour within the
OL,19,FPSNI, I became aware of the worrying
OL,20,Flevels of wider misogyny."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,FMr Boutcher has repeatedly lamented
OL,7,Fthe financial difficulties being faced
OL,8,Fby the force, and said the PSNI will
OL,9,F"sweat our asset of resource", but
OL,10,Ffunding restraints limited their
OL,11,Fcapacity in coping with serious crimes.
OL,13,F"The College of Policing recommends
OL,14,Fthat each major investigation team
OL,15,Fthat deal with murders against these
OL,16,Fyoung women, should have six cases per
OL,17,Fteam; we have 20," he said.
OL,19,F"So, I worry about that pressure."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@]O]uD@AOUyD@RO]{D@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,FHe added: "Orders that women obtain to
OL,7,Fmanage the predatory and unacceptable
OL,8,Fbehaviours of previous partners need
OL,9,Fto be enforced.
OL,11,F"Our offender management situation,
OL,12,Fand we've alluded to this in front of
OL,13,Fthis board before, we should have one
OL,14,Fofficer having 50 cases ` that
OL,15,Fincludes violent and sexual offenders
OL,16,F` we've got one to over 100."
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,FSinn Fein MLA and policing board
OL,7,Fmember Linda Dillon referred to the
OL,8,Fnumber of women killed, saying "we
OL,9,Fcannot any longer tolerate it being
OL,10,Fsomething that's on the agenda but is
OL,11,Fnot being prioritised", as she asked
OL,12,Fabout training for officers in this
OL,13,Farea.
OL,15,F"I think the policing focus needs to
OL,16,Fbe on ensuring that orders, harassment
OL,17,Forders, stalking orders, are very much
OL,18,Fproperly prioritised with regards to
OL,19,Fperpetrator activity," Mr Boutcher
OL,20,Freplied.
OL,26,@pD@`OUsD@VO]wD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,F"The actual conduct of the men who
OL,7,Fcommitted these murders goes way, way
OL,8,Fback before the police are involved,
OL,9,Fit does, that's the reality of this,
OL,10,Fthis is a societal issue."
OL,12,FThe Chief Constable further said
OL,13,Fstudent officers have "incredible and
OL,14,Fcomplex training" that includes
OL,15,F"lessons on understanding domestic
OL,16,Fabuse, the definitions, the
OL,17,Flegislation, barriers from victims to
OL,18,Fleaving relationships".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@ZO]uD@WOUvD@QO]wD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
