PN,44210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,FHe added: "It deals with non-fatal
OL,7,Fstrangulation, stalking, including
OL,8,Fharassment.
OL,10,F"They get instruction on trauma-
OL,11,Finformed approaches and the cycle of
OL,12,Fabuse that we see all too often and of
OL,13,Fcourse, often previously unrecognised,
OL,14,Fthe need to understand the impacts on
OL,15,Fchildren and safeguarding children,
OL,16,Fand includes inputs from advocacy
OL,17,Fgroups such as Women's Aid."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
