PN,44211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,FAn independent review on sexism in the
OL,7,Fforce was conducted by Rachel Langdale
OL,8,FKC, as a report earlier this month
OL,9,Ffound predatory behaviour features in
OL,10,F30% of the most serious cases
OL,11,Finvestigated by the Police Ombudsman
OL,12,Ffor Northern Ireland.
OL,14,FLast year a former PSNI officer was
OL,15,Farrested by police ombudsman
OL,16,Finvestigators on suspicion of
OL,17,Fcommitting more than 10 non-recent
OL,18,Foffences, including rape, other sexual
OL,19,Foffences between 2000 and 2009 while
OL,20,Fhe was a serving officer.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,FThe Chief Constable accepted the
OL,7,Ffindings and recommendations of the
OL,8,FLangdale review in full and pledged
OL,9,Fthat "clear and measurable action"
OL,10,Fwill be taken.
OL,12,F"I commissioned this report to ensure
OL,13,Fwe strengthen how we deal with
OL,14,Fdomestic violence, violence against
OL,15,Fwomen and girls and misogyny," he said.
OL,17,F"I wanted an independent look at our
OL,18,Fculture, our systems and processes,
OL,19,Fand for the report to identify
OL,20,Fmeaningful and sustainable mechanisms
OL,21,Ffor improvement.
OL,26,@qD@FOUqD@bO]tD@AOUwD@^O]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775160364
OL,3,CPSNI chief: Investigators face triple
OL,4,Cworkload amid violence against women
OL,6,F"Rachel makes clear that she
OL,7,Fencountered evidence of misogyny in
OL,8,Fthis police service.
OL,10,F"Let me repeat here the message I have
OL,11,Frepeatedly shared and again shared
OL,12,Fwith the entire organisation in a
OL,13,Fvideo last week ` there is no place in
OL,14,Fthis organisation for any misogyny,
OL,15,Fsexism or hateful behaviour in any
OL,16,Fform towards any colleagues from
OL,17,Fanyone.
OL,19,F"It is unacceptable and it will not be
OL,20,Ftolerated."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU{D@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/14
